1
00:00:47,840 --> 00:00:48,920
Hey!

2
00:00:48,920 --> 00:00:51,079
Oh

3
00:00:51,880 --> 00:00:53,440
my! V-Venus!

4
00:00:53,440 --> 00:00:55,239
I mean, Saturn!

5
00:00:55,239 --> 00:00:56,519
Are you okay?

6
00:00:56,519 --> 00:00:58,159
Oh dear, look at this.

7
00:00:58,519 --> 00:00:59,400
Aunt Tammy.

8
00:01:00,280 --> 00:01:01,519
Don't help him.

9
00:01:02,239 --> 00:01:03,239
This little bit of pain

10
00:01:04,119 --> 00:01:06,480
is nothing compared to what you did to my brother.

11
00:02:21,960 --> 00:02:23,639
Let me help wash your back.

12
00:02:59,679 --> 00:03:00,960
What are you doing?

13
00:03:05,280 --> 00:03:06,079
Don't!

14
00:03:08,840 --> 00:03:09,639
Bend over.

15
00:03:28,440 --> 00:03:29,679
Madame

16
00:03:29,679 --> 00:03:31,960
I've asked the banquet manager.

17
00:03:32,239 --> 00:03:33,440
He clearly confirmed

18
00:03:34,119 --> 00:03:36,239
that no extra staff were hired.

19
00:03:36,639 --> 00:03:37,840
They are all our people.

20
00:03:38,320 --> 00:03:39,559
Does this mean Lookkai was lying?

21
00:03:40,119 --> 00:03:41,400
I'm not entirely sure yet.

22
00:03:41,400 --> 00:03:42,400
But one thing is certain

23
00:03:42,400 --> 00:03:44,159
after drinking that glass of water,

24
00:03:44,159 --> 00:03:46,000
Khun Venus completely vanished.

25
00:03:46,000 --> 00:03:46,960
And what about Saturn?

26
00:03:49,039 --> 00:03:50,719
Khun Saturn's case is even worse.

27
00:03:51,519 --> 00:03:52,920
There are no clues at all.

28
00:03:53,239 --> 00:03:54,920
Except for his luggage

29
00:03:54,920 --> 00:03:56,800
and some missing clothes.

30
00:03:58,119 --> 00:03:59,199
Oh, Lord

31
00:03:59,199 --> 00:04:00,840
Whatever happens

32
00:04:01,920 --> 00:04:02,920
please don't let anything bad

33
00:04:02,920 --> 00:04:04,079
happen to my grandsons.

34
00:04:04,559 --> 00:04:06,760
I have no one else left in this life.

35
00:04:15,360 --> 00:04:16,639
Khun Pakin...

36
00:04:16,639 --> 00:04:17,760
please, stop.

37
00:04:18,519 --> 00:04:19,280
I can't take this anymore.

38
00:04:20,360 --> 00:04:21,480
But if you want to do something to me...

39
00:04:21,480 --> 00:04:22,679
just do it.

40
00:04:23,880 --> 00:04:24,760
Hey

41
00:04:25,519 --> 00:04:27,239
it's me.

42
00:04:27,920 --> 00:04:29,960
Oh boy...

43
00:04:29,960 --> 00:04:32,000
you've really been beaten to a pulp,haven't you?

44
00:04:32,000 --> 00:04:34,679
You're completely traumatized.

45
00:04:35,119 --> 00:04:35,619
Here

46
00:04:36,039 --> 00:04:38,960
eat. You're hungry, right?

47
00:04:39,440 --> 00:04:39,940
Mm

48
00:04:40,519 --> 00:04:42,000
Hurry up and eat.

49
00:04:42,000 --> 00:04:43,960
If Pakin comes back, you'll starve again.

50
00:04:43,960 --> 00:04:44,920
Um

51
00:04:46,199 --> 00:04:48,840
Whoa, whoa... eat slowly.

52
00:04:48,840 --> 00:04:50,440
You're going to choke to death.

53
00:04:50,719 --> 00:04:52,480
What's the rush?

54
00:04:57,079 --> 00:04:57,840
You know

55
00:04:58,559 --> 00:04:59,840
seeing you eat like this

56
00:05:01,360 --> 00:05:02,760
reminds me

57
00:05:05,800 --> 00:05:07,119
of the first day

58
00:05:07,760 --> 00:05:09,719
Pakin and Pakinai

59
00:05:10,679 --> 00:05:11,800
came to me.

60
00:05:12,760 --> 00:05:14,679
They were both starving.

61
00:05:16,960 --> 00:05:17,960
Plus,

62
00:05:18,239 --> 00:05:19,960
they were completely

63
00:05:20,320 --> 00:05:22,440
battered by the local kids.

64
00:05:23,639 --> 00:05:25,000
Messed up, both of them.

65
00:05:27,199 --> 00:05:28,599
Especially the older one.

66
00:05:28,599 --> 00:05:30,239
Kin was... wow.

67
00:05:30,559 --> 00:05:31,840
Messed up all over.

68
00:05:31,840 --> 00:05:33,719
Covered in wounds.

69
00:05:33,840 --> 00:05:36,239
Pakinai actually had it better.

70
00:05:36,599 --> 00:05:38,639
Do you know why?

71
00:05:41,480 --> 00:05:44,039
Kin loves his brother.

72
00:05:44,039 --> 00:05:46,159
So he protected him.

73
00:05:46,360 --> 00:05:48,480
Taking the pain so
his brother wouldn't have to.

74
00:05:53,199 --> 00:05:54,760
Those two really love each other,
don't they?

75
00:05:55,239 --> 00:05:56,679
Oh

76
00:05:57,039 --> 00:05:59,559
they'd literally die for each other.

77
00:06:00,199 --> 00:06:00,840
Mm

78
00:06:02,199 --> 00:06:02,920
Aunt Tammy.

79
00:06:03,559 --> 00:06:04,440
Why are you feeding him?

80
00:06:07,159 --> 00:06:08,039
If you're so hungry

81
00:06:08,320 --> 00:06:09,199
pick it up and eat it.

82
00:06:09,880 --> 00:06:10,519
Khun Pakin!

83
00:06:10,519 --> 00:06:11,639
What the hell is wrong with you?!

84
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:13,679
Why do you have to do this to me?

85
00:06:16,320 --> 00:06:17,000
Kin!

86
00:06:17,000 --> 00:06:17,920
Do you seriously intend

87
00:06:17,920 --> 00:06:20,480
to let him die right here?!

88
00:06:21,760 --> 00:06:22,519
Aunt Tammy

89
00:06:23,159 --> 00:06:24,320
Have you forgotten...

90
00:06:25,320 --> 00:06:26,760
who did this to us first?

91
00:06:37,079 --> 00:06:37,599
Yeah.

92
00:06:38,480 --> 00:06:39,440
Honestly, today

93
00:06:39,440 --> 00:06:41,320
I don't even know what I want to eat.

94
00:06:42,079 --> 00:06:43,360
All I know is

95
00:06:43,360 --> 00:06:45,400
I want to eat you.

96
00:06:46,400 --> 00:06:47,159
Tell you what

97
00:06:47,519 --> 00:06:49,320
I'll get dressed and
wait for you to pick me up.

98
00:06:50,159 --> 00:06:51,960
Okay, see you. Mwah.

99
00:06:58,239 --> 00:06:59,960
Why is he knocking so damn much?

100
00:07:01,119 --> 00:07:02,159
Saturn

101
00:07:02,920 --> 00:07:03,679
what did I do wrong?

102
00:07:04,800 --> 00:07:05,719
Honestly?

103
00:07:05,719 --> 00:07:06,880
You didn't do anything wrong.

104
00:07:07,119 --> 00:07:08,280
You're just boring.

105
00:07:12,360 --> 00:07:13,639
Can I have another chance?

106
00:07:14,320 --> 00:07:15,920
Can we start over?

107
00:07:15,920 --> 00:07:16,960
Whatever you want me to be

108
00:07:16,960 --> 00:07:18,159
I can be it for you.

109
00:07:18,880 --> 00:07:20,360
Do you remember what I told you?

110
00:07:21,159 --> 00:07:22,480
Even my own life

111
00:07:23,400 --> 00:07:25,000
I can give it to you.

112
00:07:28,639 --> 00:07:29,880
If I ordered you to go die

113
00:07:29,880 --> 00:07:31,159
would you do it?

114
00:07:32,840 --> 00:07:34,320
If you ordered me to go die

115
00:07:35,320 --> 00:07:36,920
I'm ready to die for you.

116
00:07:38,360 --> 00:07:39,639
Then do it.

117
00:07:39,639 --> 00:07:40,800
Prove it to me.

118
00:07:40,800 --> 00:07:41,840
Go.

119
00:07:42,079 --> 00:07:43,159
Go die.

120
00:08:07,480 --> 00:08:09,119
Hey! Hey!

121
00:08:09,119 --> 00:08:09,760
Pakinai

122
00:08:09,760 --> 00:08:10,400
Pakinai

123
00:08:11,599 --> 00:08:13,039
Stay with me

124
00:08:13,039 --> 00:08:16,279
I won't let you die.
Do you hear me?

125
00:08:17,880 --> 00:08:19,039
Wake up!

126
00:08:22,279 --> 00:08:23,439
You killed my brother!

127
00:08:24,439 --> 00:08:24,939
Pakin!

128
00:08:24,960 --> 00:08:25,460
Pakin!

129
00:08:26,199 --> 00:08:27,399
That's enough, Pakin!

130
00:08:27,399 --> 00:08:28,359
Enough, please!

131
00:08:28,880 --> 00:08:29,439
Oh my god.

132
00:08:33,239 --> 00:08:35,079
Why does it have to be like this

133
00:08:37,439 --> 00:08:38,399
Are you okay?

134
00:08:38,680 --> 00:08:40,039
Saturn

135
00:08:40,439 --> 00:08:41,199
Damn it!
